value:
$nMPID_ルーナ|Guess I inherited a bit of my mother's
awkwardness, huh... Wait, you heard
that? Forget I said anything, or else!

$nMPID_ルーナ|There wasn't anything like this where
I'm from. It was a world full of deathly
chill and unending despair...

$nMPID_双界ティアモ|I've prepared something special for
Selena, but it can wait until we've
delivered our gifts to everyone else.

$nMPID_双界ティアモ|If it gets cold, Selena and I can huddle
under my cape. That should be warm
enough for the both of us.

$nMPID_双界ティアモ|I'm keeping my expectations in
check. May he stay warm this winter,
whether I can be there or not.

I've been entrusted with a gift for
you. Go on, take it!

$nMPID_ルーナ|As long as we work together, there's
nothing we can't do!

$nMPID_双界ティアモ|I can't explain why, but sometimes it
feels like Selena and I are perfectly in
sync. Almost like we've met before...

$nMPID_ルーナ|Brrr... This isn't fair in the slightest!
How do you expect me to fight when
my hands are frozen solid?

$nMPID_ルーナ|Hey, we're the gift givers here, not
you! That said, it's not like I don't
appreciate this...

I'm Cordelia, and I'm on a mission
with Selena to deliver cheer. Let's
make this festival one to remember!

$nMPID_ルーナ|OK, that should be just about all the
gifts... Hey, are you still messing
around with my outfit? Give it a rest!$k$p$nMPID_双界ティアモ|But it's just too cute! To be honest,
I'm a little jealous that you can get
away without wearing a breastplate...$k$p$nMPID_ルーナ|What are you talking about? You'd
look amazing with or without one,
just like me!$k$p$nMPID_双界ティアモ|Oh, um... I'll admit, it's hard to argue
when you say it with such conviction.
Still, do you really think so?$k$p$nMPID_ルーナ|Well, duh. There's no way my mother
could look anything less than perfect
in this or any other getup.$k$p$nMPID_双界ティアモ|Your who? Oh well, never mind
that. Let's just make sure these final
gifts get delivered before sundown!
$nMPID_二人|It's a beautiful night!

$nMPID_二人|"It's time!"
"I know!"
$nMPID_双界ティアモ|Got something for you.
$nMPID_ルーナ|I hope you're happy...
I'm freezing...
I'll cheer you on!
Keep it together.

• "It's going to be..."
• "...an incredible night!"

• "Look at the snow!"
• "It's gorgeous..."

• "I'm enjoying these outfits. You look great, Selena."
• "Oh, shut up. You know you look better."
Why not?
Sounds like fun.
Sure, let's go.

$nMPID_双界ティアモ|The winter festival...
How lovely. *sigh*

$nMPID_ルーナ|Don't give me a sigh. It makes
me think you'd rather be
somewhere else.

$nMPID_双界ティアモ|No, it's not that! I'm sorry. I was just...
thinking about someone.

It'd be nice to walk through these
glittering streets together, but...
it was only a thought.

I don't think he'd really want to
spend this occasion with me.
$nMPID_ルーナ|I think I know who you mean...
$nMPID_双界ティアモ|What? Did you say something?
$nMPID_ルーナ|No, no. That sounds rough, though.

I can't really relate. I have an easy
time getting men to fawn over me.

$nMPID_双界ティアモ|Ahaha. Well, OK. I believe it. You are
very cute, Selena.
$nMPID_ルーナ|Yeah, I know. I get it from my mother.

She was beautiful, smart, talented...
Everybody said she was perfect.

$nMPID_双界ティアモ|I can tell by the way you say it that
you really love her.

$nMPID_ルーナ|Yeah, I... I guess I do. So much so that
I got her a present. Here, this is
for you.
$nMPID_双界ティアモ|Wait, what? Are you saying...

$nMPID_ルーナ|Now, come on. We've got a lot of
other gifts to deliver tonight.
Let's get moving!

$nMPID_双界ティアモ|Selena, wait! She really is quite a
mysterious girl. Still, I can't help
but feel close to her, somehow...
